title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: When trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row, an exception is thrown.
OB: When exporting data from a table containing a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Add a table with a group row that has a highlight rule and a map rule.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data.
